OL,3,CChilean football club unveils former
OL,4,CBarca player as knight on horseback
OL,6,FArturo Vidal's return to Colo-Colo
OL,7,Fcomes nearly 20 years after he started
OL,8,Fhis football career with the club
OL,9,F(Credit: X/@ColoColo)
OL,11,FFormer Barcelona and Juventus
OL,12,Ffootballer Arturo Vidal has been
OL,13,Funveiled in spectacular fashion before
OL,14,Ffans of his new Chilean club side.
OL,16,FVidal, 36, returned to Santiago-based
OL,17,Foutfit Colo-Colo earlier this month,
OL,18,Fhaving started his career at the club
OL,19,Fnearly 20 years ago.
