OL,3,CChilean football club unveils former
OL,4,CBarca player as knight on horseback
OL,6,FTo mark his return, Colo-Colo arranged
OL,7,Ffor the midfielder to be flown by
OL,8,Fhelicopter into its Monumental
OL,9,FStadium, on Wednesday, while tens of
OL,10,Fthousands of fans cheered him on.
OL,12,FVidal was then paraded in front of
OL,13,FColo-Colo supporters as he rode a
OL,14,Fhorse, wearing a crown and holding a
OL,15,Fsword.
