OL,3,CChilean football club unveils former
OL,4,CBarca player as knight on horseback
OL,6,FHe later told the crowd it was
OL,7,F"wonderful to see the stadium full for
OL,8,Fa welcome", adding: "I don't remember
OL,9,Fwhat I was thinking about the
OL,10,Fhelicopter, there were a lot of
OL,11,Femotions.
OL,13,F"The Colocolino fans made me feel
OL,14,Floved."
OL,16,FVidal enjoyed a decorated career in
OL,17,FEurope between 2007 and 2022, playing
OL,18,Ffor the likes of Italian giants
OL,19,FJuventus and Spanish side FC Barcelona.
